<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 01:52:57 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>Coinbase 陷入亏损，收入再次下降</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-07/coinbase-swings-to-a-loss-while-posting-another-revenue-drop</link><description>就在宣布大幅裁员和推动人工智能发展几天后，Coinbase Global Inc. 表明其财富与加密货币市场的联系有多么紧密。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iPgaPKxTDp9g/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 20:29:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-07/coinbase-swings-to-a-loss-while-posting-another-revenue-drop</guid></item><item><title>战略的比特币威胁隐藏着一个丑陋的真相</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-05-07/strategy-s-bitcoin-threat-hides-an-uglier-truth</link><description>数字资产国库正在寻求利润提升&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/is.35pDwYKdA/v8/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-05-07/strategy-s-bitcoin-threat-hides-an-uglier-truth</guid></item><item><title>币安称财政部已就交易所监管发出信函</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-07/binance-says-treasury-sent-letter-over-monitorship-of-exchange</link><description>据一位知情人士透露，近三年前，币安同意接受监管，同时承认美国对制裁和反洗钱违规行为的指控。币安收到了美国财政部的一封信，要求采访该加密货币交易所的员工并记录其记录，以调查潜在的制裁违规行为。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iJPv5.ht42Eg/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 18:04:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-07/binance-says-treasury-sent-letter-over-monitorship-of-exchange</guid></item><item><title>Kraken 母公司将以 6 亿美元收购 Reap Technologies</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-07/kraken-parent-to-buy-reap-for-600-million-in-asian-expansion</link><description>加密货币交易所 Kraken 的所有者已同意向 Reap Technologies 支付 6 亿美元，Reap Technologies 是一家面向稳定币的跨境和商业支付服务提供商。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i4rqC37VOMHg/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 12:01:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-07/kraken-parent-to-buy-reap-for-600-million-in-asian-expansion</guid></item><item><title>Kalshi 在 Coatue 领投的一轮融资中获得 220 亿美元估值</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-07/kalshi-secures-22-billion-valuation-in-coatue-led-round</link><description>Kalshi Inc. 已完成一轮融资，该预测市场平台的估值达到 220 亿美元，大约是五个月前估值的两倍。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iWtmvv51zsUQ/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 13:53:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-07/kalshi-secures-22-billion-valuation-in-coatue-led-round</guid></item><item><title>波兰 Crypto MAGA 赞助商的消亡引发政治愤怒</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-07/demise-of-crypto-maga-sponsor-in-poland-sparks-political-furor</link><description>波兰最大的数字资产交易平台的垮台给唐纳德·特朗普在总统府的盟友带来了麻烦。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iM5dz4UcSL9s/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 12:37:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-07/demise-of-crypto-maga-sponsor-in-poland-sparks-political-furor</guid></item><item><title>蓝猫头鹰准备第一支基金购买二手私人信贷</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-07/blue-owl-preps-its-first-fund-to-buy-secondhand-private-credit</link><description>据一位知情人士透露，Blue Owl Capital 正准备推出首次信贷二级市场策略，并正在与该基金的潜在投资者进行早期谈判。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i3YKD.88He1Y/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 10:55:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-07/blue-owl-preps-its-first-fund-to-buy-secondhand-private-credit</guid></item><item><title>华尔街公司发布了数十个加密货币职位——但有一个问题</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-07/wall-street-firms-post-dozens-of-crypto-jobs-with-a-catch</link><description>在加密货币简历中拥有华尔街的影子已经成为保持高薪就业的一种方式。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ijhNLZA0oZ04/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 10:15:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-07/wall-street-firms-post-dozens-of-crypto-jobs-with-a-catch</guid></item><item><title>与特朗普家族有联系的比特币矿商连续第二个季度亏损</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-06/trump-family-linked-bitcoin-miner-posts-second-consecutive-quarterly-loss</link><description>美国比特币公司是特朗普家族支持的矿商，去年在最大的数字资产从历史高点暴跌之前成立，在其持有的价值下跌后，该公司连续第二个季度亏损。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/itrP8ZGdUt_4/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 May 2026 21:10:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-06/trump-family-linked-bitcoin-miner-posts-second-consecutive-quarterly-loss</guid></item><item><title>Strategy 的 Saylor 表示可能转向比特币销售</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-06/bitcoin-btc-holder-strategy-will-never-say-never-to-selling-reserves</link><description>Strategy Inc. 正在削弱其永远不会出售其持有的 670 亿美元比特币的想法。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iHeGwBJsXcoQ/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 May 2026 05:02:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-06/bitcoin-btc-holder-strategy-will-never-say-never-to-selling-reserves</guid></item><item><title>摩根士丹利首次推出加密货币交易，价格低于竞争对手</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-06/morgan-stanley-debuts-crypto-trading-undercuts-rivals-on-price</link><description>摩根士丹利正在其 E*Trade 平台上推出加密货币交易，并讽刺竞争对手：价格更便宜。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i2jiKmJEeTcI/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 May 2026 11:45:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-06/morgan-stanley-debuts-crypto-trading-undercuts-rivals-on-price</guid></item><item><title>拥抱人工智能，否则就会落后：加密货币公司纷纷裁员</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-05/embrace-ai-or-get-left-behind-job-cuts-sweep-through-crypto-firms</link><description>加密货币和支付公司一系列与人工智能相关的裁员给分析师和投资者带来了一个好奇的问题：如何评估人工智能部分是否真实？ &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iWniLtHgFScg/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 19:41:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-05/embrace-ai-or-get-left-behind-job-cuts-sweep-through-crypto-firms</guid></item></channel></rss>